Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.51,0:21:37.42,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}梦中所见的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.64,0:21:44.58,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}被遗忘在原处  渐渐化作了黑白相片
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.75,0:21:49.05,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}从视界中消失
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.99,0:21:56.34,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}但你总是目不转睛地注视着明天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.50,0:22:02.12,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}究竟要付出多少泪水为代价？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.22,0:22:08.94,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}所以你也能将我们的迷惘化作坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.38,0:22:15.42,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}解放紧密相连的心灵——
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.75,0:22:21.87,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}Believe  这份满溢而出的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.16,0:22:28.52,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}In the dreaming  只为某人而存在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.04,0:22:34.42,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}凭借这份微小的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.24,0:22:40.08,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}不管风会有多么猛烈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.38,0:22:47.64,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}我都想要守护你
